{
  "stem": "2830.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then we saw a path going.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we walked through that path to lead us someplace.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "When we walked out, it was a field of, you know, officers training on horses.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So my sister was panic.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She thought they-- they come and-- to-- to-- to, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That they saw me-- I don't even-- I don't know if they saw us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But she panicked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she said, you wanted to leave.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I was afraid, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So she said, you wanted to leave.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She just throw me down.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she said, you wanted to leave.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she grabbed me, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Angry at me that I wanted to leave-- why she didn't went with the parents or-- or--",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--or went to, you know, the-- on that to Kowel, to the concentration camp back, you know, like everybody else did.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, they-- eventually they turned around-- those-- those officers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had enough training.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They just turned around, and they went their way.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 132,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The didn't saw me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 132,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was about quite a distance.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But you saw them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was quite--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--a distance.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 135,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And even if they saw, they probably wouldn't know who it is--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 136,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--yet.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 137,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But we always had in that mind, you know, that everybody who is gonna see you--",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 138,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--will kill-- will kill you because you're Jewish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 138,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So then it was easier on-- on her.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 138,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said, OK.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 138,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I brushed off.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 138,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we started again.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 138,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We started walking.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 138,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was no end to that walk.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 138,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was just field.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 139,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was already going to get dark.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 139,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we didn't know where-- we are going to wind up in another forest?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 139,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Finally, we turned-- we turned on another, you know, path we saw.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 139,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we started to this, but where it's gonna lead us?",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
